UK House Price Index (HPI) Dataset
----------------------------------

This project uses the official UK House Price Index (HPI) dataset.

Source:
UK Government – HM Land Registry
https://www.gov.uk/government/statistical-data-sets/uk-house-price-index-data-downloads-january-2024

Direct CSV Link (Latest Full File):
https://www.gov.uk/government/statistical-data-sets/uk-house-price-index-data-downloads-january-2024
Notes:
- File is too large to upload to GitHub (63+ MB)
- Download manually using the link above
- Place the CSV file in the project’s /data/ folder before running the notebook
